com.android.test

Interface BundleTest

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyBundleTestCase

    public interface BundleTest
    Implement this interface to receive a Bundle containing the command line arguments passed to the test runner into your JUnit3 test.

    The test runner will call injectBundle(Bundle) after object construction but before any TestCase#setUp() methods are called. Note the order in which injectBundle is called vs other inject methods is not defined.

    Declaring this in a JUnit4 test will have no effect. Use InjectBundle instead.
